Nigerian afrobeat artiste, Benjamin Nnayereugo Best, better known by his stage name “Killaboy” ,has shared photos of his trip to Maldives in an exclusive business class flight. The Umuahia- born singer, who has been enjoying fast acceptance among music lovers, has been dubbed the new huspuppi on the account of his wealth and lifestyle. The ‘cure your boredom’ crooner is among the new crop of artists bursting the airwaves. Killaboy has stated in a previous interview he loves to explore as he often draws inspiration for his songs from his various vacations. 